that's pretty much
how he became a legend.

11
00:01:34,512 --> 00:01:38,683
Thirty years later, a kid named
Benjamin Franklin Rodriguez...

12
00:01:38,808 --> 00:01:40,810
became a neighborhood legend.

13
00:01:40,935 --> 00:01:43,104
It was in the greatest summer
of my life...

14
00:01:43,188 --> 00:01:45,106
when he taught me
to play baseball,

15
00:01:45,190 --> 00:01:47,400
and he became my best friend.

