00:08:59,916 --> 00:09:03,420
Oh, I'm sorry, Mom.
It was an accident.

85
00:09:12,762 --> 00:09:16,016
Scotty, have you made
any friends yet?

86
00:09:17,642 --> 00:09:20,061
- No.
- Why not, honey?

87
00:09:22,147 --> 00:09:24,149
'Cause I'm still new.

88
00:09:24,274 --> 00:09:28,528
I don't want you sitting around in here
all summer fiddling with this stuff...

89
00:09:28,653 --> 00:09:30,655
